    Black Aracnia looked to Quickstrike, a foul look crossed her face. She 
came all the way here and he gave her an attitude. Big mistake.
    "You can stay in here, on your ass, or you can go and see Darkmouse. She 
should be waking up by now. It would be nice if you were there, but dont. I 
dont think she would want to see you in such a selfish state." She snapped, 
and then left to the lab to greet Darkmouse when she woke.
